    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK777">
<l>cuḻalu micaivēṇṭi vēṇṭā vuyirār</l>
<l>kaḻalyāppuk kārikai nīrttu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The fastening of an ankle-ring by those who desire world-wide renown and not (the safety of) their lives is like adorning (themselves).</l>
            </lg>
